&lt;p&gt;Senior Social Worker&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a part time experienced social worker to join a small team of senior social workers based at the Pembridge Palliative Care Centre. The successful candidate will be expected to work as a member of the multidisciplinary team contributing to its understanding of the psychological, emotional and social problems that may be experienced by individuals and families facing death and bereavement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be expected to hold a case load providing a service to patients and families across the service i.e community, day hospice, inpatients, offering a palliative care social work service to residents of south Brent, Hammersmith and Fulham, Kensington and Chelsea and Westminster&lt;/p&gt;
